# [1.0.0]

## Changed 
- Migrated the code to uv. 
- Rewrote the entire code to be simpler. 
Quotes will be stored in quotes.json. Random list will be stored in a separate file. 
Edit/Add quotes directly by editing quotes.json file. No extra config or params required 

